decks.notes: This deck focuses on aggressive gameplay with the goal of overwhelming the opponent quickly. It utilizes the Cascade mechanic to gain card advantage and tempo, constantly pressuring the opponent with powerful spells. The deck also incorporates a variety of lands to ensure consistent mana production. The main creatures in the deck are Shardless Agent and Scion of Draco, both contributing to the card advantage and threatening the opponent's life total. The deck also includes disruptive elements with Force of Negation and Subtlety, preventing opponent's plays and maintaining control. Overall, the deck aims to dominate the board early on and secure victory before the opponent can stabilize.
